name: Rhythm
description:
Rhythm is a set of useful nodes to help your Revit project maintain a good rhythm with Dynamo. Rhythm is authored by John Pierson (@60secondrevit) of Parallax Team (http://www.parallaxteam.com/) and designtechunraveled.com. 

Supported Revit versions are 2019-2023, with supported Dynamo versions being 2.0.4 - 2.13.x
